lines.speaker: daxter
lines.text: Do you remember how to jump?

lines.speaker: agent
lines.text: Stay sharp, we've got a tough part of town coming up.

lines.speaker: ashelin
lines.text: Payback's a bitch, and I'm it.

lines.speaker: ashelin
lines.text: Watch your ass, I'm only woman on the outside.

lines.speaker: ashelin
lines.text: Let me knock you down to size...

lines.speaker: ashelin
lines.text: Small guns don't get me going.

lines.speaker: ashelin
lines.text: You don't know who you're dealing with.

lines.speaker: ashelin
lines.text: I never said you could touch me there.

lines.speaker: ashelin
lines.text: Hit me again and you'll lose something

lines.speaker: ashelin
lines.text: Listen, buddy, whose side are you on?

lines.speaker: ashelin
lines.text: Do that again and I'll put you down.

lines.speaker: ashelin
lines.text: Learn to control your gun, buddy.

lines.speaker: ashelin
lines.text: Maybe I should be behind you.

lines.speaker: ashelin
lines.text: Another one like that and you'll be

lines.speaker: ashelin
lines.text: Man, there are a lot of 'em!

lines.speaker: ashelin
lines.text: There's some more of those things!

lines.speaker: ashelin
lines.text: You were right, Jak. What my father's doing

lines.speaker: ashelin
lines.text: is wrong. I need to help fix this.

lines.speaker: ashelin
lines.text: If you get to the Weapons Factory, maybe we can

lines.speaker: ashelin
lines.text: stop him. I'll meet you there.

lines.speaker: ashelin
lines.text: I think now's the time to act.

lines.speaker: ashelin
lines.text: The Metal Heads are so focused on attacking

lines.speaker: ashelin
lines.text: the city, they may have left their nest vulnerable.

lines.speaker: torn
lines.text: Jak, you've got to get out to the Wasteland

lines.speaker: torn
lines.text: and breach the nest barrier any way you can.

lines.speaker: torn
lines.text: Maybe if you get inside and take out the Metal Head leader

lines.speaker: torn
lines.text: the army will collapse. It's a long shot,

lines.speaker: torn
lines.text: but it might be our only chance.

lines.speaker: torn
lines.text: I think you should practice more.

lines.speaker: torn
lines.text: Jak, this is Torn. The Underground needs good drivers

lines.speaker: torn
lines.text: for our vehicle missions. Prove your skills on the

lines.speaker: torn
lines.text: ring challenge and maybe we'll let you in on the action.

lines.speaker: torn
lines.text: Not bad, I think we can use ya.

lines.speaker: torn
lines.text: Here's a little reward for your effort.

lines.speaker: baron
lines.text: My shield is impervious to your attacks!

lines.speaker: baron
lines.text: There is nothing you can do!

lines.speaker: baron
lines.text: Your Dark Eco powers surprise me!

lines.speaker: baron
lines.text: Your arrogance will be your downfall!

lines.speaker: baron
lines.text: I grow tired of this, now you die!

lines.speaker: baron
lines.text: You cannot run away from these!

lines.speaker: baron
lines.text: Allow me to share the pain!

lines.speaker: baron
lines.text: The stone is mine! Let me show you what it can do!

lines.speaker: baron
lines.text: Now you see the stone's power in capable hands!

lines.speaker: baron
lines.text: I have all the power I need!

lines.speaker: baron
lines.text: I am the city's savior, not you!

lines.speaker: baron
lines.text: You idiot, you're no match for me!

lines.speaker: baron
lines.text: Give up and I'll make it painless!

lines.speaker: baron
lines.text: You can do better than that!

lines.speaker: baron
lines.text: You really think you have a chance?

lines.speaker: baron
lines.text: I should have killed you long ago!

lines.speaker: baron
lines.text: Go back to wherever you came from!

lines.speaker: baron
lines.text: You're both going to die by my hand!

lines.speaker: baron
lines.text: Impressive, but let's try that again!

lines.speaker: baron
lines.text: You could never be a baron!

lines.speaker: baron
lines.text: Hm, I expected more from you!

lines.speaker: baron
lines.text: Sorry, old boy, it's just war!

lines.speaker: baron
lines.text: Too bad you don't have what it takes!

lines.speaker: baron
lines.text: We're similar, Jak... oh, except you're dead!

lines.speaker: baron
lines.text: Feel the fury of the Precursor Stone!

lines.speaker: baron
lines.text: With the stone's power, I am invincible!

lines.speaker: baron
lines.text: My little friends will take care of you!

lines.speaker: baron
lines.text: I have better things to do than waste my time with you!

lines.speaker: baron
lines.text: Not bad, but let me show you what real power is!

lines.speaker: daxter
lines.text: Please tell me you remember how to roll...

lines.speaker: oracle
lines.text: Bring me 200 more Metal Head Skull Gems

lines.speaker: oracle
lines.text: and I will show you another Dark Power.

lines.speaker: oracle
lines.text: and another power will be yours to control.

lines.speaker: oracle
lines.text: Bring me more Skull Gems to receive control

lines.speaker: oracle
lines.text: You do not have enough Skull Gems.

lines.speaker: oracle
lines.text: Come back when you have collected more.

lines.speaker: oracle
lines.text: Trust not your reliance on weapons.

lines.speaker: oracle
lines.text: Use only your body and brain for this challenge.

lines.speaker: oracle
lines.text: You must not use weapons in this challenge.

lines.speaker: vin
lines.text: Okay, the B-Zone Power Grid is back online.

lines.speaker: vin
lines.text: Have fun being killed in the Palace.

lines.speaker: vin
lines.text: You destroyed the last of the Metal Head eggs!

lines.speaker: vin
lines.text: That should give us a little more eco for the city.

lines.speaker: vin
lines.text: You still haven't gotten all the Metal Head eggs!

lines.speaker: vin
lines.text: Make sure you get 'em all, or I'm gonna have

lines.speaker: vin
lines.text: Thank goodness you blew up those wells.

lines.speaker: vin
lines.text: I sure don't want any more Metal Heads coming around here.

lines.speaker: vin
lines.text: Good work, boys! I owe ya one.

lines.speaker: vin
lines.text: Good work, guys! The fewer Metal Head eggs

lines.speaker: vin
lines.text: we allow to hatch, the fewer of those nasty monsters

lines.speaker: vin
lines.text: Once again you guys have saved my butt!

lines.speaker: vin
lines.text: Maybe now I'll get a raise. Or a long vacation.

lines.speaker: vin
lines.text: God knows I could use one. Thanks for the help!

lines.speaker: vin
lines.text: The shield wall is down! I repeat - the shield wall is down!

lines.speaker: vin
lines.text: I knew Metal Heads would be the end of me!

lines.speaker: vin
lines.text: OH NO! Metal Heads are at the door!!

lines.speaker: vin
lines.text: Too many of them!! Jak!!! AHHHH!!!

lines.speaker: youngsamos-before-rescue
lines.text: Excellent work, boys! Come on back to the Hideout,

lines.speaker: youngsamos-before-rescue
lines.text: I have another task for you.

lines.speaker: youngsamos
lines.text: We'll all sleep a little easier tonight.
